---

<section class="bg-background py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 font-serif text-3xl font-semibold text-foreground md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        Tudo que você precisa em uma única plataforma
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
        As funcionalidades mais avançadas do mercado para transformar sua prática clínica
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="mb-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-secondary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-secondary">Essencial</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">
            Teleconsulta Integrada
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Atendimento online com vídeo HD, gravação com consentimento e prontuário integrado.
            Não precisa sair da plataforma.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-secondary/40 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-secondary text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-secondary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-secondary">Certificado</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">
            Prontuário Eletrônico Completo
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            SOAP, evolução, anamnese, CID-10. Em conformidade com CFM 1.821/2007 e LGPD.
            Busca instantânea por histórico.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-primary">Validade Legal</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">
            Assinatura Digital Certificada
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Receitas, atestados e laudos com assinatura digital ICP-Brasil.
            Validade jurídica garantida em todo território nacional.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-secondary/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-secondary/40 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-secondary text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-secondary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-secondary">Automação</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">
            WhatsApp Business Integrado
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Confirmações, lembretes e gestão de grupos de pacientes.
            API oficial do WhatsApp com disparo em massa aprovado.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-primary">Marketing</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">
            Automação de Redes Sociais
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Agende posts para Instagram, Facebook e LinkedIn.
            Gerencie sua presença digital profissional sem sair da plataforma.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-secondary/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-secondary/40 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-secondary text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-secondary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-secondary">Documentos</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">
            Receitas e Laudos Profissionais
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Templates personalizados para receitas médicas, laudos psicológicos,
            atestados e relatórios. Geração automática em PDF.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-primary">Convênios</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-card-foreground">
            Integração TISS
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Padrão TISS completo para faturamento com convênios.
            Geração automática de guias e envio para operadoras de saúde.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-secondary/10 to-primary/10 p-8 text-center">
        <p class="mb-4 font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">
          + Mais de 30 funcionalidades incluídas
        </p>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground">
          Gestão financeira, relatórios personalizados, integração com Google Calendar,
          portal do paciente, faturamento automatizado, controle de estoque e muito mais.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
